Program: Omnibus
Title: Northen Ireland
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jz7
Last Broadcast Date: 08 November 1990
A look back over the years of The Troubles and speculation at what the future holds for Northern Ireland as people grow weary of the violence of the 20 year 'low level war'. Interviewees include Peter Robertson and Bishop Edward Daly.